@startuml 03-seq-auth
' docs/uml/03-seq-auth.puml
' Sequence diagram: Login + Refresh Token Rotation + Protected Request with RLS.
' Что показывает: три флоу аутентификации — логин, ротацию refresh-токенов с reuse detection, и запрос с RLS.
' Кому полезна: backend-разработчикам и security-аудиторам.

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333
    LifeLineBorderColor #666
    ParticipantBorderColor #333
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8EAF6
    ParticipantFontSize 13
    NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
}

participant "Browser" as Browser #E3F2FD
participant "Traefik" as Traefik #F3E5F5
participant "NestJS API" as API #E8F5E9
database "PostgreSQL\n(RLS)" as DB #FFF3E0
database "Redis" as Redis #FFEBEE

== Flow 1 — Login ==

Browser -> API : POST /auth/login\n{ email, password, tenantSlug }
activate API

API -> DB : SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE email = $email\nAND tenant_id = (SELECT id FROM tenants WHERE slug = $slug)
DB --> API : user { id, passwordHash, role, tenantId }

API -> API : bcrypt.compare(password, passwordHash)

alt password invalid
    API --> Browser : 401 { message: "Invalid credentials" }
else password valid
    API -> API : sign accessToken (JWT, 15min)\nsub=userId, tenantId, role
    API -> API : sign refreshToken (JWT, 30d)\nsub=userId, tokenId=uuid
    API -> Redis : SET refresh:{userId}:{tokenId}\nvalue={ used: false }\nEX 2592000 (30 days)
    Redis --> API : OK
    API --> Browser : 200 { accessToken, refreshToken, user }
end

deactivate API

== Flow 2 — Refresh Token Rotation ==

Browser -> API : POST /auth/refresh\n{ refreshToken }
activate API

API -> API : jwt.verify(refreshToken)\nextract: userId, tokenId

API -> Redis : GET refresh:{userId}:{tokenId}
Redis --> API : tokenData

alt token not found (expired/revoked)
    API --> Browser : 401 { code: "TOKEN_EXPIRED" }
else token.used === true (REUSE DETECTED!)
    note right of API #FFCDD2
        Compromised token!
        Wipe all sessions.
    end note
    API -> Redis : DEL refresh:{userId}:*\n(all sessions for user)
    Redis --> API : OK
    API --> Browser : 401 { code: "TOKEN_REUSE_DETECTED" }
else token.used === false (valid)
    API -> Redis : SET refresh:{userId}:{tokenId}\nvalue={ used: true }
    note right of Redis : Mark old token as used
    Redis --> API : OK

    API -> API : sign NEW accessToken (15min)
    API -> API : sign NEW refreshToken (30d)\nnew tokenId=uuid

    API -> Redis : SET refresh:{userId}:{newTokenId}\nvalue={ used: false }\nEX 2592000
    Redis --> API : OK

    API --> Browser : 200 { accessToken, refreshToken }
end

deactivate API

== Flow 3 — Protected Request with RLS ==

Browser -> Traefik : GET /projects\nAuthorization: Bearer {accessToken}
Traefik -> API : forward (api.app.localhost → :3000)
activate API

API -> API : JwtAuthGuard: verify JWT\nextract { sub, tenantId, role }

API -> API : TenantMiddleware:\nextract tenantId from JWT payload

API -> DB : SELECT set_config(\n'app.tenant_id', '{tenantId}', true)
note right of DB #E8F5E9
    RLS now active:
    all queries auto-filter
    by tenant_id
end note
DB --> API : OK

API -> DB : SELECT * FROM projects
note right of DB : RLS policy filters:\nWHERE tenant_id = app.tenant_id
DB --> API : [ ...tenant-scoped projects ]

API --> Traefik : 200 [ ...projects ]
Traefik --> Browser : [ ...projects ]

deactivate API

@enduml
